thread.title: D’Metris W.

author: D’Metris W.
title: D’Metris W.
text: At first I was a little hesitant to go with Custom USB, after sourcing companies to assist us with conference materials. I must say...we were not only pleased with the outcome of the products received (printed USB lanyards) but I was amazed at the attentiveness and quick action from the staff I worked with. Thank you again for making our largest conference to date, also the BEST! The lanyards were a hit! We look forward to using you in the future...
